    skos:scopeNote "This minor head will include the Cost of printing of Govt. Publications, Codes, manuals etc. and their distribution including charges of Book Depots. The Cost of printing of Text Books will be recorded under the major head \"2202-Education\"."@en .

lmmha:2058-00-800 a skos:Concept ;
