lmmha:2875-01-107 a skos:Concept ;
    dct:identifier "2875-01-107" ;
    dct:source "LMMHA note 1, part2d.htm"@en ;
    dct:type "Minor Head"@en ;
    skos:broader lmmha:2875-01 ;
    skos:inScheme lmmha:scheme ;
    skos:prefLabel "Ghazipur Opium Factory"@en ;
    skos:scopeNote "These minor heads will have the following sub-heads with suitable detailed heads thereunder: - Working Expenses- Management Purchase of Opium Repairs and Maintenance Buildings Machinery and Equipment Suspense Transfer to Depreciation Reserve Fund Other expenditure Deduct-Value of Opium transferred to Alkaloid Works The sub-head \"Other expenditure\" will include pensions / gratuities and interest on capital and contributions to Funds. The sub-head \"Management\" will include proportionate expenditure of Bureau of Narcotics recorded under the minor head \"Narcotics Control\" below the major head \"2070-Other Administrative Services\"."@en .

