    skos:prefLabel "Other Loans to Electricity Boards"@en ;
    skos:scopeNote "Loans to Electricity Boards and other parties earmarked for identifiable thermo-electric (excluding diesel), diesel and Hydro-electric power and their transmission and distribution will be accounted for under the minor heads, \"Thermal Power Generation\", \"Diesel/gas power generation\", \"Hydel Generation and \"Transmission and Distribution\" respectively. Other loans to Electricity Boards, not identifiable with any of these minor heads will be accounted for under the minor head \"Other Loans to Electricity Boards\"."@en .

