lmmha:8659-00-140 a skos:Concept ;
    dct:identifier "8659-00-140" ;
    dct:source "LMMHA note 6, part4j.htm"@en ;
    dct:type "Minor Head"@en ;
    skos:broader lmmha:8659 ;
    skos:inScheme lmmha:scheme ;
    skos:prefLabel "Miscellaneous Suspense"@en ;
    skos:scopeNote "This head will be sub- divided into :- For sub-heads (i) and (ii) please see note on Sub-head (l) and (m) below Note (3) below the major head \"8658-Suspense Accounts\". Sub-head (iii) will be operated where NDF collections appear as deductions from salary bills etc. of Government servants. This head will be cleared by issue of Cheques / Bank Drafts in favour of the Reserve Bank of India."@en .

